{
  "texts": [
    "Here are some key points to consider [9,10]: Opportunities 1.",
    "Knowledge Access: Large language models have access to vast amounts of medical literature, research papers, clinical guidelines, and other relevant sources.",
    "They can quickly retrieve and synthesize information, enabling healthcare providers to access a wealth of knowledge to aid in diagnosis and treatment decisions. 2.",
    "Diagnostic Support: Language models can assist pathologists and other healthcare professionals in analyzing digital pathology images.",
    "They can help identify patterns, highlight potential abnormalities, and provide additional insights based on existing medical knowledge."
  ]
}